{"word":"G1549 - ἔκγονον - ékgonon - ek'-gon-on - Nephew","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἔκγονον</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">ékgonon</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ek'-gon-on</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Nephew</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"பிளந்தது, பேரன் பேத்தி - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"sprung from one, born, begotten"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Neuter of a derivative of a compound of <a href=\"#/G1537 - ἐκ - ek - ek/1537\">G1537</a> and <a href=\"#/G1096 - γίνομαι - gínomai - ghin'-om-ahee/1096\">G1096</a>; a <i>descendant</i>, that is, (specifically) <i>grandchild:</i> - nephew.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}